| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1780 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5799336c-a9b2-5a24-bee9-b5bd8b3d83bd"
